#Brazilian Caipirinha 


It is a delicious drink from Brazil which is quite popular all aeound the world. 

Recipe:

1)- One Lemon
2)- 50 ml of Brazilian cachaça
3)- Four spoons of white sugar
4)- 5 ice cubes

How to prepare: 

First of all, cut the lemon into slices and put these slices in a cup along with the white sugar
after that smach till the get next add the cachaça and the ice cubs mix a little bit more
and finally the drink is ready and I hope is delicious :)


